➜当艺术变为葡萄酒
http://www.sohu.com/a/426370443_100347	63197
<p>Whem the ART become WINE</p>
<p>The very first wine with a unique handmade marble rose designed by an Italian artist was officially presented in China in the Italian Embassy to China in Beijing at the last edition of the “Italian Cuisine and wine week in the world”</p>
<p>在最后一届“世界意大利美食与葡萄酒周”上，由意大利艺术家设计的首款带有独特手工大理石玫瑰的葡萄酒在中国北京意大利驻华大使馆正式亮相。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201022/0b551c196294402b9766c13ffcbd8ca7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>The name of the wine “Antica Realtà” corresponds with the name of the first artistic period (1997-2008) of the Italian artist Simone Filosi. The artist chooses the rose (his main leit-motiv) to create this special design for the wine in which every rose is Handmade in Italy. The wine chosen is very unique thanks to the use of an ancient and very unique grape of black Muscat from Asti that gives great intensity and aromas to the wine.</p>
<p>葡萄酒“Antica Realtà”的名称与意大利艺术家西蒙尼·菲洛的第一个艺术时期(1997-2008)的名称相一致。这位艺术家选择了玫瑰(他的创作的主旋律)来创作这款葡萄酒的特别设计，每一朵玫瑰都是在意大利手工制作的。选用的葡萄酒非常独特，这要归功于阿斯蒂产区的特殊黑色莫斯卡托葡萄，这是一种古老的无性繁殖葡萄，能够赋予葡萄酒极大的色彩和味道。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201022/a2537db5c11f4a90bd660b09b6afb0da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
