</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>The artist draws inspiration from the Rose, a flower that always and forever is the Universal Symbol of the highest Human feeling. The mystery of beauty enclosed in that flower pushes Simone to sculpt a marble rose, trying to restore to the inert stone the freshness, the delicacy, the wonderful lightness of this flower.</p>
<p>西蒙尼从玫瑰中获得灵感，这是一朵永远是人类最高情感——爱情的普遍象征之花。这朵花所蕴含的美丽与神秘推动着西蒙尼雕刻了一朵大理石玫瑰，并试图将这朵花的清新、精致、那近乎美妙的轻盈以及它的脆弱复活到一块木讷的石头上。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201022/3399d1f02df245de831b1c8d39e98cde.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Every single rose present in every bottle in hand-carved in Italy with real Italian marble.</p>
<p>瓶身上的每一朵玫瑰花都是用意大利大理石手工雕刻而成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201022/52ac8aca87c54727b8bdb6f4468687a4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>女模-Alessia Sargentini</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201022/fc20e8e3a94a4da7beff8f1de8e95cee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>男模-Federico Seymour Fagioli</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201022/cbc05cc138e1416592dab3ffbfd577e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Tasting notes: Brilliant and intense rosè colour. Intensely aromatic at the nose, fresh with rose and red fruits notes. Sweet, full and velvet taste. Its aftertaste is very intense and the grapes aroma and flavour are clearly perceptible.</p>
<p>品酒辞：明亮而强烈的玫瑰色。香气浓郁，带有玫瑰和红色水果的清新气息。甜甜的，饱满的，如天鹅绒般柔软。回味十分浓郁，有明显的葡萄香气和风味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201022/0de8d246ed554c11bb37ab84f28a775d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Pairing: Fruits, desserts, cakes, cookies and cocktails.</p>
<p>搭配推荐：这款酒完美搭配水果，甜点，蛋糕，饼干和鸡尾酒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201022/75e0fccc948f4cc6a903dba29a44c906.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>The 100% handmade in Italy, designed by the Artist Simone Filosi and only available in the official shop of 100ITA in JD.com.</p>
<p>这款由艺术家西蒙娜·菲洛西(Simone Filosi)设计的100%意大利手工雕刻的艺术葡萄酒 只能在京东“100ITA官方旗舰店”购买。</p>